# üöÄ Space Invaders - Pygame Edition

A simple Python implementation of the classic Space Invaders game using Pygame.



## Features
- Player movement with arrow keys
- Enemy wave generation
- Shooting mechanics
- Score tracking
- Collision detection

## Requirements
- Python 3.6+
- Pygame library

## Quick Start
```bash
pip install pygame
python space_invaders.py
Controls
Key	Action
‚Üê ‚Üí	Move spaceship
SPACE	Fire laser
ESC	Quit game
How to Customize
Edit player_size to change spaceship size

Modify enemies list to adjust difficulty

Change color values (RGB) for visual customization

Troubleshooting
If you get ModuleNotFoundError:

bash
Copy
pip install pygame --upgrade


